{"type": "article", "id": 4181, "title": "Fragment Design x Beats by Dre 耳机", "description": "", "date": "2014-12-08T07:41:49Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 15, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605233128TwofSK20PbvGi9nx.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t音响制造商 Beats by Dre 又推出了艺术家合作款，这一次与其搭档的是日本时装设计师藤原浩的品牌 Fragment Design 。藤原浩此前曾是一名 DJ ，这也使得这次合作备受期待。双方联手带来了一款耳机与音响，两款产品选用了银白色作为产品的主色调，搭配以 Fragment Design 品牌标志性的蓝色，呈现出酷酷的味道。这两款联名产品今日将上架苹果官网及苹果各零售店铺，定价 1598 元，<a href=\"http://store.apple.com/us/accessories/beats\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233127I9Cg6JR1kmxjr0Aw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233128kXzTEOjDeygcUxG8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}